  <official_title>Randomized Double--‐Blinded, Controlled Trial to Compare the Effectiveness of Sugammadex vs. Placebo to Prevent Residual Neuromuscular Block in the Post--‐Anesthesia Care Unit as Evaluated With a Non--‐Invasive Respiratory Volume Monitor</official_title>
